Test automation framework using REST ASSURED with Java, TestNG and Maven
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  This project demonstrates REST ASSURED for API testing ,
and how it can be used with Java, TestNG.
   
1  For data source excel sheet is used. (\src\main\java\com\qa\testdata\Assurity_TestData.xlsx)
2. For reporting testNG reporting utility is used.
3. Also Extended reporting is used for better looking,readable reports.
   These reports can be seen at: /test-output/Extent.html
4. To run the tests use the following command:
    mvn clean test
5 . Or it can be run from the testNG.xml file.   
5. Logs can be found in /application.log.
